data.description: More photos coming soon. Don't miss out on  this 3 beds 1.5 bath home in the desirable Brookfield section of Cherry Hill. This multi-level home is one of the largest models in the neighborhood. Recently renovated Kitchen to include stainless, granite, tile backsplash, shaker style cabinetry, and tile flooring..  Newer hardwood flooring throughout the main and upper levels. The backyard is perfect for entertaining, comes with a pool, deck, fire pit and all the space you need for a large gathering. Newer roof,  water heater, and lots of storage space. There are 3 ample size bedrooms and two baths. Easy access to 295, shopping and eateries. Call to schedule your private tour!
